Insights.TitleConsideredVisits: Considered rows having a growth of at least %s%% compared to %s.
Insights.TitleConsideredChanges: Considered movers only if they increased or decreased by more than %s visits, new entries only if they increase by more than %s visits, and disappeared rows if they decreased by more than %s visits based on %s total visits.
Insights.TitleReportBasedOn: Based on %s %s, rows less than %s %s were ignored
Insights.TitleIgnoredChanges: Changes affecting less than %s visits were ignored.
Insights.TitleConsideredMoversAndShakers: Visits changed from %s to %s compared to %s. Based on this an evolution of each row of %s%% is expected.
Insights.TitleConsideredChangesMoversAndShakers: Considered movers only if they grew by more than %s%% visits or less than %s%% visits, new entries only if they increased by more than %s%% visits (%s), and disappeared rows if they descreased by less than %s%% visits (%s)
